  N5 --> N6[UI: UI Screen (dashboard) - Surface consolidated plan and KPIs on planner dashboard for review]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Optimized shift rosters and contingent worker placements written to SAP S/4HANA; training assignments scheduled; reduced overtime and COGS variance; maintained or improved OTIF and fewer line stoppages.]
